data.comment: Get-ChildItem -Path $env:TEMP\checkoutuow | ForEach-Object -Begin { $checkoutItems = [System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary[string,string[]]]::new() } -Process { $checkout = ($_ | Select-String -Pattern "([^\s\)\(]+)(?=.*\(checkout\))").Matches.Value | Sort-Object -Unique; $elements = ($_.BaseName | Select-String -Pattern '[^\s\(\)]+' -AllMatches).Matches.Value; $elements | ForEach-Object { $checkoutItems.Add($_,$checkout); } } -End { $checkoutItems } | Export-Clixml -Path $env:OneDriveCommercial\checkoutUowItems.xml $checkoutItemsPerProgram = [System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary[string,hashtable]]::new() $checkoutItemsPerProgram['B_IFM'] = $checkoutItems

data.comment: $Programs = 'B_IFM', 'CH604PROD', 'CTALPROD', 'LJ4045PROD', 'GXPROD' $query = @' SELECT DISTINCT StateValue, StateName, Remark FROM FiniteStateMachineState '@ $statesPerProgram = [System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary[string, pscustomobject]]::new($Programs.Count) foreach ($Program in $Programs) { $connectionInfo = $dbConnections.connections.info | Where-Object -FilterScript { $_.serviceName -match ($Program -replace '_').Substring(0, 2) } | Select-Object -First 1 $sqlClOut = Write-Output "SET SQLFORMAT JSON`n$query" | SQLcl -S "***REMOVED***@$($connectionInfo.hostname):$($connectionInfo.port)/$($connectionInfo.serviceName)" | Join-String -Separator $([Environment]::NewLine) $sqlOutErrSplit = $sqlClOut | Select-String -Pattern '(?ms)(?<json>{.*})(?<err>.*)' | Select-Object -ExpandProperty Matches $sqlOut = $sqlOutErrSplit.Groups['json'].Value | ConvertFrom-Json $states = $sqlOut.results.items $stateNames = [System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary[int, pscustomobject]]::new($states.Count) foreach ($statevalue in $states.statevalue) { $stateNames.Add([int]::Parse($statevalue), ($states | Where-Object { $_.statevalue -eq $statevalue } | Select-Object -ExcludeProperty statevalue)) } $statesPerProgram.Add($Program, $stateNames) }
